@startuml cicd-workflow
!pragma activityFlow
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam activityBorderColor #333333
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #F0F0F0
skinparam activityDiamondBorderColor #333333
skinparam arrowColor #333333
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam noteBorderColor #F9A825
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title CI/CD Workflow Overview - GitHub Actions

|#palegreen|**Workflow: ci.yml**|
start
note right
**Trigger:** push | pull_request
**Branches:** main, java-angular, feat/**, feature/**, fix/**, refactor/**, docs/**, test/**, chore/**, perf/**, ci/**
**Jobs:** backend + frontend (always)
end note
:**CI**
(backend: Gradle test + JaCoCo
 frontend: typecheck → lint → test → build);
stop

|#orange|**Workflow: codeql.yml**|
start
note right
**Trigger:** push | pull_request + cron (weekly)
**Branches:** main, java-angular, feat/**, feature/**, fix/**, refactor/**, docs/**, test/**, chore/**, perf/**, ci/**
**Schedule:** cron: '20 5 * * 3' (Wed 05:20 UTC)
end note
:**codeql**
(trigger: push | pull_request + cron
 + matrix: java-kotlin + javascript-typescript);
stop

|#lightskyblue|**Workflow: e2e-nightly.yml**|
start
note right
**Trigger:** cron + workflow_dispatch
**Schedule:** cron: '0 2 * * *' (02:00 UTC daily)
end note
:**e2e-nightly**
(Playwright visual regression);
stop

legend right
| Workflow | Trigger | Color |
| ci | push / pull_request | #palegreen |
| codeql | push / pull_request / cron | #orange |
| e2e-nightly | cron / dispatch | #lightskyblue |
endlegend
@enduml
